description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare Evil Eye Edition!

Welcome to November and the best in paranormal talk radio!

Today, Dave & Tim explore haunted sites around the world and share creepy tales of the ghosts that walk our realm. A ghostly prank ends in tragedy, we explore The Evil Eye and its remedies, a famous Hollywood Horror House is for sale and a ghost hunter suffers a "paranormal hangover".

PLUS your emails, stories, questions, comments and more!
